00:08:33.140 --> 00:08:35.080
I've copied scriptures for Princess Ying.

00:08:35.930 --> 00:08:38.910
I pray she ascends to bliss swiftly.

00:08:39.370 --> 00:08:40.470
I didn't expect you

00:08:40.490 --> 00:08:44.230
to come to my Xuanguang Hall of your own accord.

00:08:48.050 --> 00:08:49.560
I'm merely grieving

00:08:50.610 --> 00:08:51.680
for Her Highness.

00:08:52.850 --> 00:08:53.830
I heard

00:08:54.900 --> 00:08:57.320
Her Highness was regaining her senses.

00:08:57.700 --> 00:08:59.030
But after Your Majesty's visit,

00:08:59.930 --> 00:09:01.710
she passed away.

00:09:05.580 --> 00:09:07.080
My Ying

00:09:08.220 --> 00:09:10.150
was always improving and relapsing.

00:09:11.050 --> 00:09:12.000
I never thought

00:09:12.220 --> 00:09:13.910
His Majesty would cause her death.

00:09:14.250 --> 00:09:15.150
I understand.

00:09:16.140 --> 00:09:17.790
Your Majesty had no choice.

00:09:18.410 --> 00:09:20.830
You didn't want Ying to suffer longer in this world.

00:09:25.810 --> 00:09:27.350
I don't understand

00:09:28.290 --> 00:09:29.350
