00:09:30.220 --> 00:09:31.590
you mean.

00:09:35.370 --> 00:09:37.000
The late Emperor died suddenly,

00:09:37.460 --> 00:09:39.230
followed by the fire at Luling Palace,

00:09:39.540 --> 00:09:42.590
leaving Princess Ying deranged.

00:09:44.490 --> 00:09:45.560
Her life

00:09:46.580 --> 00:09:48.120
has been full of hardship.

00:09:49.020 --> 00:09:50.760
What exactly brings you

00:09:51.780 --> 00:09:53.470
here today?

00:09:55.370 --> 00:09:56.710
Since my youth,

00:09:57.900 --> 00:09:59.320
I've served at His Majesty's side.

00:10:01.930 --> 00:10:03.680
I wanted to serve

00:10:05.180 --> 00:10:07.280
a wise ruler who could bring hope

00:10:07.300 --> 00:10:08.560
to Great Qi.

00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:10.830
Indeed.

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:14.870
You've always been loyal to him.

00:10:14.890 --> 00:10:17.160
But now I no longer wish to be.

00:10:22.650 --> 00:10:24.230
I want to help you

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:27.990
eliminate your real threat.

00:10:30.010 --> 00:10:31.230
I intend to aid the Prince of Yuzhang

00:10:31.730 --> 00:10:33.110
in seizing the throne.

00:10:35.490 --> 00:10:36.320
Why?

00:10:40.700 --> 00:10:41.560
Why?

00:10:44.770 --> 00:10:46.160
Perhaps it's because

00:10:47.890 --> 00:10:48.990
I've been betrayed.

00:10:51.580 --> 00:10:53.680
You give everything to someone,

00:10:55.130 --> 00:10:57.230
yet he drifts further away

00:10:57.580 --> 00:10:59.350
for an unworthy cause.

00:11:00.580 --> 00:11:01.870
Disappointment turns

00:11:02.490 --> 00:11:03.590
to hatred over time.

00:11:05.250 --> 00:11:06.470
Then, hatred festers

00:11:07.820 --> 00:11:09.320
until you want him gone.

00:11:12.850 --> 00:11:14.280
Surely, you must know

00:11:17.730 --> 00:11:19.350
that feeling.

00:11:21.820 --> 00:11:23.160
I don't understand

00:11:23.850 --> 00:11:25.800
your intentions.

00:11:37.850 --> 00:11:40.560
Do you know what you're saying?

00:11:40.700 --> 00:11:41.830
Unless you do this,

00:11:42.460 --> 00:11:43.590
the Prince of Yuzhang's heart

00:11:43.940 --> 00:11:46.040
will always be with his brother.

00:11:46.530 --> 00:11:48.400
You'll never win it back.

00:11:56.820 --> 00:11:58.710
You must fan the flames of his resentment toward His Majesty.

00:11:59.890 --> 00:12:01.280
Turn the brothers against each other

00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:03.110
unto death.

00:12:03.460 --> 00:12:05.710
Only then will he fight for the throne.

00:12:08.890 --> 00:12:10.750
Princess Ying's death

00:12:11.580 --> 00:12:13.710
has lit the first fire.

00:12:16.220 --> 00:12:17.710
But it's not enough.

00:12:24.700 --> 00:12:25.990
What do you mean?

00:12:27.700 --> 00:12:30.080
Does Your Majesty dare to stake your life?

00:12:40.010 --> 00:12:41.590
I have a poison here.

00:12:41.940 --> 00:12:42.750
Upon taking it,

00:12:42.890 --> 00:12:43.560
