00:12:43.820 --> 00:12:45.710
and pulse quickly cease,

00:12:45.890 --> 00:12:47.470
plunging you into a deathlike trance

00:12:47.770 --> 00:12:49.400
while you remain fully conscious.

00:12:49.650 --> 00:12:50.990
The antidote

00:12:51.530 --> 00:12:54.230
will revive you in moments from that sham death.

00:13:03.340 --> 00:13:04.320
This slice of ginseng

00:13:04.940 --> 00:13:07.080
has been pre-soaked in the antidote.

00:13:07.650 --> 00:13:09.320
You can have a trusted aide

00:13:09.460 --> 00:13:12.110
