00:19:48.730 --> 00:19:49.550
Xiao Qianqing,

00:19:50.770 --> 00:19:52.360
calm yourself and think this through.

00:19:52.620 --> 00:19:54.450
Doesn't Ying's death seem suspicious?

00:19:56.220 --> 00:19:57.400
